I’ve introduced legislation with @TinaSmithMN to ensure child care centers have the resources to be safe and healthy places for our children during this pandemic and beyond—and to give child care workers the support they need.

https://twitter.com/ewarren/status/1276946540385505281 QT @ewarren We’re on the verge of a child care crisis. If we don't act now, millions of parents will be unable to return to work as the economy begins to restart and our recovery will suffer. 

@TinaSmithMN and I have a plan to fix it. Here’s how we’re going to do it: http://pbs.twimg.com/media/EbiSz-EXgAEiFQl.jpg https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/1276930365928738816/vid/480x270/RbC9O5Y2MHPBItCU.mp4?tag=13
